item.title: Everytime u get error it comes like this or somethin client.java:5892: ';'
item.dc:creator: @Javacisnotrecognized _^_
item.description:
@Javacisnotrecognized wrote:

That’s the line number. Client.java:1 would mean it’s on the first line, client.java:708836224 would mean it’s on the 708836224th line, etc. That’s why most text editors come with CTRL+G for going to lin numbers
